WEBVTT

01:38.229 --> 01:40.509
[Fate Chooses You]

01:41.539 --> 01:43.630
[Episode 3]

01:46.759 --> 01:47.280
Miss.

01:48.070 --> 01:49.280
This road is difficult,

01:49.280 --> 01:50.400
and there are landslides.

01:50.400 --> 01:52.060
This road is full of potholes.

01:52.120 --> 01:53.120
You're all alone.

01:53.120 --> 01:55.150
If you fall,
there's no one to help you up.

01:55.150 --> 01:56.880
You should find an easier path.

01:57.479 --> 01:59.210
Come on, let's get back to work.

02:08.030 --> 02:09.120
Excuse me, gentlemen.

02:09.120 --> 02:10.449
Could you please tell me

02:10.560 --> 02:11.960
how to get to the capital?

02:14.430 --> 02:15.400
The restaurant owner said

02:15.400 --> 02:16.560
there was an inn nearby.

02:16.560 --> 02:18.220
Why haven't we reached it yet?

02:18.280 --> 02:19.030
There hasn't been a single place

02:19.030 --> 02:20.230
to rest along the way.

02:24.520 --> 02:25.520
Is it red or green?

02:27.430 --> 02:28.560
The book says colors

02:28.800 --> 02:31.200
should appear after the flesh is replaced.

02:32.150 --> 02:33.550
Why isn't it working yet?

02:34.400 --> 02:35.400
It should be soon.

02:39.620 --> 02:42.190
[Outskirts of the capital]

02:50.590 --> 02:52.470
Who dares block the road? Move aside!

02:52.470 --> 02:54.430
Is that the
Head Clerk of the Central Secretariat,

02:54.430 --> 02:55.360
Song Qingbao, in the carriage?

02:55.360 --> 02:56.710
How dare you block the road

02:56.710 --> 02:58.000
when you know full well
who's in the carriage?

02:58.000 --> 02:59.400
I have questions for him!

03:03.000 --> 03:04.850
[Liang Wenjing, Chen Zhi,
Zhou Yifu, Zhao Qian]

03:03.780 --> 03:05.180
Are these names correct?

03:05.750 --> 03:06.150
Yes!

03:06.280 --> 03:06.840
Yes, exactly!

03:06.840 --> 03:07.710
It's them!

03:08.680 --> 03:10.140
I have noted all the names.

03:10.750 --> 03:11.950
Go back and tell them:

03:11.960 --> 03:13.190
if they have any final wishes
or last words,

03:13.190 --> 03:14.400
let them settle their affairs quickly.

03:14.400 --> 03:15.530
When the time comes,

03:15.680 --> 03:17.210
I will come for their lives.

03:17.910 --> 03:18.560
All right.

03:20.190 --> 03:21.250
Please let me down!

03:44.630 --> 03:45.430
Finally here.

03:48.310 --> 03:49.510
There are officials.

03:52.960 --> 03:54.820
He's in a bounty guard's uniform.

04:11.710 --> 04:12.150
Halt!

04:16.560 --> 04:17.160
Do you

04:17.680 --> 04:18.880
come from Wei County?

04:20.600 --> 04:22.060
What can we do for you, Sir?

04:22.190 --> 04:23.720
What's your business here?

04:25.310 --> 04:26.310
We're merchants.

04:26.430 --> 04:27.120
Merchants?

04:27.830 --> 04:29.600
Merchants in what kind of trade?

04:29.600 --> 04:31.720
I travel with our boss,

04:31.950 --> 04:32.920
buying and selling goods.

04:32.920 --> 04:34.430
We sell turbans, colored garments,

04:34.430 --> 04:37.390
seasonal flowers and fruits, boots,
shoes, bowls, and dishes.

04:37.390 --> 04:39.120
If you're itinerant peddlers,

04:39.390 --> 04:40.720
where is your carriage?

04:42.000 --> 04:42.870
The Ghost Festival is approaching.

04:42.870 --> 04:44.390
We plan to go to the next town

04:44.390 --> 04:45.950
to buy peach and willow branches,

04:45.950 --> 04:47.450
cattail leaves, and five-colored
plague papers for resale.

04:47.450 --> 04:48.480
As for the carriage,

04:48.480 --> 04:50.810
we'll arrange that when we reach the town.

04:54.680 --> 04:56.610
Do you have further business, Sir?

04:57.430 --> 04:58.690
Here's the situation.

04:58.920 --> 05:00.750
I'm a bounty guard
from Dongzhou Prefecture.

05:00.750 --> 05:01.600
I took on a bounty

05:01.600 --> 05:02.950
and came here to arrest someone.

05:02.950 --> 05:03.560
But the target

05:03.560 --> 05:04.390
holed up in that inn

05:04.390 --> 05:05.310
and won't come out.

05:05.310 --> 05:06.750
I can't make a move inside,

05:06.750 --> 05:08.390
so I've been stuck waiting out here.

05:08.390 --> 05:09.790
The longer this drags on,

05:10.040 --> 05:11.510
the more I've burned through my funds.

05:11.510 --> 05:13.170
I can barely afford meals now.

05:13.600 --> 05:14.310
Gentlemen,

05:14.870 --> 05:16.530
could you lend me some silver?

05:17.070 --> 05:18.160
I'll repay you in full

05:18.160 --> 05:20.890
once I complete the mission
and claim the bounty.

05:27.680 --> 05:28.120
Here,

05:28.480 --> 05:29.480
this is all I have.

05:30.510 --> 05:31.600
Too much, too much!

05:31.950 --> 05:33.550
Half of this would be plenty.

05:37.230 --> 05:38.630
Let me help you with that.

05:38.690 --> 05:41.040
[In Perfect Safety]

05:38.830 --> 05:39.310
Come on.

05:39.750 --> 05:40.550
Alright then.

05:41.000 --> 05:41.600
Landlady!

05:41.920 --> 05:43.120
Come and attend to guests!

05:43.120 --> 05:44.560
Coming, coming!

05:45.070 --> 05:45.680
Sir,

05:46.070 --> 05:48.430
do you have money for a meal today?

05:46.750 --> 05:49.210
[Mrs. Li]

05:50.070 --> 05:51.680
Money is the least of my worries.

05:51.680 --> 05:52.720
I'm more concerned
that your little establishment

05:52.720 --> 05:54.520
might not have what I'm craving.

05:54.630 --> 05:56.120
As long as you pay enough,

05:56.190 --> 05:58.680
even if you want dragon meat
from the heavens,

05:58.680 --> 06:00.270
I'll slice you a portion.

06:11.040 --> 06:12.840
And who are these two gentlemen?

06:15.040 --> 06:16.630
They are big merchants from Wei County,

06:16.630 --> 06:17.720
top-tier patrons.

06:18.310 --> 06:19.640
And they're my friends.

06:21.240 --> 06:23.310
What may I address you, gentlemen?

06:23.510 --> 06:25.840
Are you here for a meal or accommodations?

06:26.120 --> 06:27.040
Accommodations.

06:27.040 --> 06:28.800
Give us a quiet prime room.

06:31.800 --> 06:33.180
The heavy rain last night

06:33.180 --> 06:34.720
leaked into the rooms on the second floor.

06:34.720 --> 06:36.870
How about a room on the 1st floor?

06:37.190 --> 06:38.159
I'll give you

06:38.240 --> 06:39.270
a discount.

06:39.830 --> 06:41.120
A discount sounds great.

06:41.120 --> 06:42.270
Then make it on the 1st floor.

06:42.270 --> 06:42.870
Landlady,

06:43.310 --> 06:44.870
also bring steamed buns, meat pies,

06:44.870 --> 06:46.070
noodle sheets, sliced soup,

06:46.070 --> 06:47.190
strong liquor, and beef.

06:47.190 --> 06:48.120
Make it quick, please.

06:48.120 --> 06:49.050
We're starving.

06:49.560 --> 06:50.220
Right away!

06:50.680 --> 06:51.310
Come, buddy,

06:51.310 --> 06:52.310
let's sit inside.

07:09.120 --> 07:10.390
Is that the guy you mentioned?

07:10.390 --> 07:10.800
Yes,

07:10.920 --> 07:11.600
that's exactly him.

07:11.600 --> 07:13.000
He committed murder
in the Prefectural City,

07:13.000 --> 07:13.870
and the authorities ordered me

07:13.870 --> 07:15.200
to bring him to justice.

07:15.310 --> 07:16.800
Go ahead and arrest him, then!

07:16.800 --> 07:17.920
Don't you see what's

07:17.920 --> 07:18.550
written on that plaque?

07:18.550 --> 07:20.750
[Safe Haven Inn:
Your Safety is Guaranteed.

07:19.000 --> 07:19.870
Do you know why this place

07:19.870 --> 07:21.240
is called "Safe Haven Inn"?

07:21.240 --> 07:22.720
This inn has a rule:

07:23.120 --> 07:23.680
whether you're

07:23.680 --> 07:25.390
a ruthless fugitive,

07:25.720 --> 07:26.830
a court criminal

07:26.830 --> 07:27.560
on the run,

07:27.680 --> 07:28.950
or a notorious bandit

07:28.950 --> 07:29.750
roaming the seas,

07:29.750 --> 07:31.120
once you enter this inn,

07:31.430 --> 07:32.760
no fighting is allowed,

07:32.830 --> 07:34.230
and no one is to be harmed.

07:35.680 --> 07:38.680
And we're just supposed to
obey whatever the inn says?

07:38.800 --> 07:39.870
If they dare make such a claim,

07:39.870 --> 07:42.070
they clearly have the means to back it up.

07:42.070 --> 07:43.000
Did you see

07:43.000 --> 07:44.630
that delicate-looking Landlady
by the door earlier?

07:44.630 --> 07:46.510
Her twin blades
are swift and impenetrable—

07:46.510 --> 07:47.640
utterly masterful.

07:48.070 --> 07:48.600
It is said

07:49.000 --> 07:51.530
that she's a disciple
of Swift Blade Hu Chuan.

07:51.680 --> 07:53.240
You know Swift Blade Hu Chuan, right?

07:53.240 --> 07:56.100
He was ranked 8th
on the List of Top Martial Artists.

07:56.310 --> 07:58.240
Though I heard he has passed away.

08:02.120 --> 08:03.580
Order up! Coming through!

08:04.870 --> 08:05.360
Gentlemen,

08:05.360 --> 08:06.920
here are your wines, dishes,

08:06.920 --> 08:07.720
steamed buns,

08:08.800 --> 08:09.430
meat pies,

08:10.120 --> 08:10.650
and beef.

08:12.390 --> 08:13.050
Attendant,

08:13.830 --> 08:14.960
I'd also like a room,

08:15.630 --> 08:16.630
right next to his.

08:16.750 --> 08:17.390
His?

08:17.630 --> 08:19.070
Well, he ran out of lodging money
days ago.

08:19.070 --> 08:20.680
Now he just eats plain noodles.

08:20.680 --> 08:21.800
With 1 bowl lasting 3 hours,

08:21.800 --> 08:23.000
he takes 4 bowls a day.

08:23.070 --> 08:24.750
The noodles have turned to mush,

08:24.750 --> 08:26.810
yet he's still clinging to that bowl.

08:26.870 --> 08:27.930
If that's the case,

08:28.040 --> 08:30.160
I might be able to return
and report success soon?

08:30.160 --> 08:30.630
Really?

08:31.800 --> 08:32.909
Order a signature dish

08:32.909 --> 08:33.970
to celebrate then!

08:34.510 --> 08:35.710
Let's just skip that.

08:35.789 --> 08:37.250
Your signature dishes are

08:37.320 --> 08:38.780
a bit too rich for my blood.

08:44.440 --> 08:45.300
That attendant

08:46.320 --> 08:47.550
is as skinny as a twig.

08:48.000 --> 08:49.630
His nickname is Cloud-Sweeper,

08:49.630 --> 08:51.750
coming from his indestructible iron palms.

08:51.750 --> 08:53.200
A few years back,

08:53.200 --> 08:55.730
he was a renowned master
in the martial world.

08:56.000 --> 08:56.910
And in the kitchen,

08:56.910 --> 08:58.110
there's a hefty cook.

08:58.390 --> 08:59.910
He's a master of external martial arts.

08:59.910 --> 09:00.870
His body is so tough,

09:00.870 --> 09:02.600
as if it were impervious
to blades and spears.

09:02.600 --> 09:04.480
Even when facing ordinary cultivators,

09:04.480 --> 09:06.540
he can give a good account of himself.

09:07.240 --> 09:08.000
How is it

09:08.000 --> 09:09.360
that you know all this so well?

09:09.360 --> 09:10.160
A few days ago,

09:10.480 --> 09:11.810
I tracked my target here

09:12.080 --> 09:13.280
and came in after him.

09:13.440 --> 09:15.150
Just like you, I didn't believe
in their rules either,

09:15.150 --> 09:17.610
and I ended up
getting into a fight with them.

09:17.840 --> 09:19.100
Did you lose the fight?

09:20.120 --> 09:21.720
Well, it wasn't that I couldn't beat them.

09:21.720 --> 09:22.980
I was still recovering

09:23.150 --> 09:24.150
from a demon toxin

09:24.550 --> 09:26.840
I had been exposed to
while hunting a fiend a few days earlier.

09:26.840 --> 09:28.100
You're a bounty guard,

09:28.150 --> 09:29.880
yet you handle demon hunts too?

09:30.320 --> 09:32.180
I've picked up bits of all trades.

09:42.550 --> 09:43.080
Let's go!

09:55.550 --> 09:56.810
Autumn Crimson Blade!

09:57.200 --> 09:59.320
I've searched for you all these years,

09:59.320 --> 10:01.080
and you've been living it up!

10:04.080 --> 10:05.340
Autumn Crimson Blade?

10:05.720 --> 10:07.320
So you're the one they call

10:07.960 --> 10:09.030
Autumn Crimson Blade, the Hellreaver—

10:09.030 --> 10:10.720
the No. 1
on the List of Top Martial Artists!

10:10.720 --> 10:12.030
Quite the reputation!

10:13.910 --> 10:14.840
Who are you then?

10:15.510 --> 10:16.440
Eight years ago,

10:16.630 --> 10:17.550
at Lei Fort,

10:18.240 --> 10:19.630
you took 27 lives.

10:20.440 --> 10:21.480
Autumn Crimson Blade,

10:21.480 --> 10:23.210
I might not have seen your face,

10:23.360 --> 10:24.150
but I remember

10:24.150 --> 10:25.280
your voice clearly.

10:25.390 --> 10:26.390
You can't deny it.

10:27.870 --> 10:28.790
Lei Fort?

10:29.870 --> 10:31.070
It's that bandit den.

10:31.240 --> 10:32.440
Did you just admit it?

10:33.720 --> 10:34.720
Yes, it was indeed my doing.

10:34.720 --> 10:35.240
Great!

10:35.550 --> 10:36.510
At least you have the guts to admit it—

10:36.510 --> 10:37.910
that makes you a real man.

10:39.030 --> 10:39.960
What do you want?

10:40.030 --> 10:41.560
I've hunted you for 8 years.

10:42.000 --> 10:43.750
Naturally, I intend to use your blood

10:43.750 --> 10:46.210
to appease the spirits
of my fallen buddies.

10:46.510 --> 10:47.510
You can't kill me.

10:48.200 --> 10:48.860
Why is that?

10:49.240 --> 10:51.440
Do you think I'd back down

10:52.000 --> 10:54.460
just because you have 2 lackeys
by your side?

10:55.600 --> 10:56.330
Can you read?

11:04.910 --> 11:06.240
What does it read there?

11:07.080 --> 11:08.080
Safe Haven Inn—

11:08.670 --> 11:10.200
Your Safety is Guaranteed.

11:10.510 --> 11:11.750
The rule of this inn

11:12.320 --> 11:14.000
is that regardless of identity or

11:14.000 --> 11:15.030
background,

11:15.320 --> 11:17.270
no violence is permitted in this inn.

11:17.270 --> 11:19.080
Break it, and you'll regret it.

11:19.390 --> 11:19.990
Am I right?

11:21.360 --> 11:22.160
He's correct!

11:24.390 --> 11:25.600
How dare you mock me?

11:34.630 --> 11:36.030
Table: 10 taels of silver each.

11:36.030 --> 11:37.790
Spoons and teacups: 1 tael apiece.

11:37.790 --> 11:39.360
Plates and bowls: two taels each.

11:39.360 --> 11:41.020
Liquor jars: four taels each.

11:41.030 --> 11:42.480
Teapots: six taels each.

11:42.750 --> 11:43.860
The rest is undamaged,

11:43.860 --> 11:45.060
so I won't charge you.

11:46.270 --> 11:48.080
The bill sums up to 36 taels of silver.

11:48.080 --> 11:48.880
Who's paying?

11:49.240 --> 11:51.320
Landlady, you are as beautiful
as a blooming flower,

11:51.320 --> 11:52.980
but you don't seem too bright.

11:53.150 --> 11:54.270
Go ask around—

11:54.910 --> 11:56.080
since when do bandits

11:56.080 --> 11:57.120
pay for anything?

11:57.670 --> 11:59.510
Others' rules don't concern me.

11:59.790 --> 12:00.750
But here,

12:01.000 --> 12:02.550
you follow my rules.

12:03.360 --> 12:04.890
What I sell isn't just food—

12:05.120 --> 12:06.030
it's safety.

12:07.360 --> 12:09.670
If any of you want bloodshed or revenge,

12:09.960 --> 12:11.480
you'll wait until this guest

12:11.480 --> 12:12.480
finishes his meal

12:12.910 --> 12:14.000
and steps outside

12:14.320 --> 12:15.390
that door.

12:23.510 --> 12:24.870
What kind of damned inn is this?

12:24.870 --> 12:26.630
Are you lecturing me about rules?

12:26.630 --> 12:27.720
What if I slaughter everyone

12:27.720 --> 12:28.600
in this shabby place today?

12:28.600 --> 12:29.320
What then?

12:29.840 --> 12:30.750
What then?

12:41.080 --> 12:41.680
Landlady,

12:41.840 --> 12:42.970
what's the verdict?

12:43.120 --> 12:44.440
Don't kill them.

12:45.340 --> 12:46.320
We need compensation.

12:46.320 --> 12:47.050
Understood!

13:07.320 --> 13:08.580
Autumn Crimson Blade,

13:08.910 --> 13:10.040
you got lucky today.

13:10.750 --> 13:11.750
Next time we meet,

13:11.870 --> 13:13.240
I won't go easy on you!

13:18.870 --> 13:19.600
Pay up.

13:22.120 --> 13:23.150
Why should I pay?

13:24.510 --> 13:26.080
You took shelter here to avoid disaster.

13:26.080 --> 13:27.480
Did you think it was free?

13:28.790 --> 13:30.270
So many people took shelter here.

13:30.270 --> 13:32.200
Why am I the only one being charged?

13:32.790 --> 13:34.720
You bear a striking resemblance

13:34.720 --> 13:35.870
to someone

13:35.910 --> 13:36.910
I once knew.

13:37.480 --> 13:38.540
His surname was Lu,

13:38.790 --> 13:39.920
and he was a painter.

13:40.320 --> 13:42.180
Might you be acquainted with him?

13:44.080 --> 13:45.440
Many people in this world

13:45.440 --> 13:46.840
share similar features.

13:48.750 --> 13:49.630
True.

13:50.560 --> 13:51.970
Eleven years ago,

13:52.000 --> 13:53.730
he looked exactly as you do now.

13:54.080 --> 13:55.320
By my reckoning,

13:55.630 --> 13:56.480
he should be

13:56.600 --> 13:58.400
considerably older these days.

14:01.960 --> 14:03.600
The total was 36 taels of silver,

14:03.600 --> 14:05.460
but I'll only charge you 30 taels.

14:31.840 --> 14:33.790
Autumn Crimson Blade!

15:10.270 --> 15:11.730
Do you confess your crime?

15:13.360 --> 15:14.790
I am the commander of Jinming Camp,

15:14.790 --> 15:17.240
the General of the Swift Cavalry
personally appointed by the Emperor!

15:17.240 --> 15:19.240
How dare you raise a hand against me?

15:23.270 --> 15:24.730
Do you confess your crime?

15:28.870 --> 15:29.720
I do.

15:30.320 --> 15:31.870
The negligence in the Wei County
famine case—

15:31.870 --> 15:33.120
it was that scoundrel Liang Wenjing

15:33.120 --> 15:34.380
who ordered me to do it!

15:35.000 --> 15:36.860
I knew Lord Lu was a good official.

15:36.870 --> 15:38.390
He only used extreme measures

15:38.390 --> 15:39.840
to save the people.

15:40.150 --> 15:41.510
But I had no choice!

15:42.080 --> 15:44.080
That old brute Liang Wenjing

15:45.200 --> 15:46.440
forced me!

15:47.630 --> 15:48.400
Guilty.

15:49.550 --> 15:50.860
Execution is hereby decreed!

15:50.860 --> 15:54.420
♪ I point to the sky,
I question the moon ♪

15:54.450 --> 15:57.440
♪ I'd rather be a wandering immortal
in the mortal world ♪

16:20.390 --> 16:20.870
Lu,

16:21.440 --> 16:22.900
do you know that Landlady?

16:23.360 --> 16:23.750
Yes,

16:24.480 --> 16:25.720
she used to be my neighbor.

16:25.720 --> 16:26.390
Neighbor?

16:28.000 --> 16:29.730
How come I don't remember that?

16:29.750 --> 16:31.240
You weren't around during that time.

16:31.240 --> 16:32.300
Then where did I go?

16:33.960 --> 16:35.760
How should I know where you were?

16:38.120 --> 16:39.440
Where was I?

16:42.720 --> 16:43.670
But still,

16:44.120 --> 16:45.200
I think Xin is wonderful—

16:45.200 --> 16:46.060
good-natured,

16:46.150 --> 16:46.750
genuine,

16:47.150 --> 16:48.200
and most importantly,

16:48.200 --> 16:49.660
the two of you are married.

16:50.480 --> 16:51.940
It wasn't a real marriage.

16:52.550 --> 16:53.200
We just did that

16:53.200 --> 16:54.330
to form a blood pact.

16:55.360 --> 16:56.620
That truly sounds like

16:56.720 --> 16:57.910
an ungrateful scoundrel

16:57.910 --> 17:00.040
who abandons others after using them.

17:01.080 --> 17:02.200
You're a hybrid of War Demons

17:02.200 --> 17:03.360
and the Human Race,

17:03.510 --> 17:04.849
burdened with the Five Deficiencies Curse.

17:04.849 --> 17:05.920
To escape this divine punishment

17:05.920 --> 17:07.000
and be reborn as human,

17:07.000 --> 17:08.460
you must pass five trials:

17:08.480 --> 17:10.030
shedding skin, replacing flesh,
renewing bones,

17:10.030 --> 17:10.960
purifying blood,
and transforming the heart.

17:10.960 --> 17:12.790
Each trial hangs by a thread
between life and death.

17:12.790 --> 17:14.349
You must find a blood relative

17:14.349 --> 17:15.640
to form a blood pact with you,

17:15.640 --> 17:17.680
linking your consciousnesses as one,

17:17.680 --> 17:19.030
so when you stand at death's door,

17:19.030 --> 17:20.349
that bond may grant you a lifeline—

17:20.349 --> 17:21.680
a chance to cheat death.

17:22.270 --> 17:23.310
You have no family,

17:23.310 --> 17:24.770
so you had to marry someone

17:24.829 --> 17:26.829
to establish this blood pact.

17:28.310 --> 17:29.000
So what?

17:29.750 --> 17:31.150
So, the marriage is real—

17:31.350 --> 17:32.640
even heaven recognizes it!

17:32.640 --> 17:34.170
By what right do you deny it?

17:34.720 --> 17:35.270
Besides,

17:35.550 --> 17:36.960
Xin is a good woman.

17:37.400 --> 17:38.860
Why are you rejecting her?

17:42.880 --> 17:43.610
Who's there?

17:45.830 --> 17:46.830
Where did they go?

18:14.390 --> 18:16.070
She's in love with someone else.

18:16.070 --> 18:18.030
She claimed she was cursed
to bring misfortune to her husband

18:18.030 --> 18:19.880
and wanted to marry a death row prisoner

18:19.880 --> 18:21.440
to dispel the bad luck—

18:21.880 --> 18:22.960
so she wouldn't harm

18:22.960 --> 18:24.290
the one she truly loves.

18:27.200 --> 18:28.460
I wasn't aware of that.

18:28.720 --> 18:29.590
This marriage

18:29.750 --> 18:31.070
was merely a deal.

18:31.510 --> 18:32.970
We each got what we needed.

18:33.070 --> 18:33.960
She and I will

18:34.510 --> 18:35.680
never meet again.

18:39.270 --> 18:40.200
It's rare to meet

18:40.680 --> 18:41.750
such a fine woman.

18:42.550 --> 18:43.210
What a pity.

18:43.830 --> 18:45.160
But she's a cultivator—

18:45.230 --> 18:46.240
she will live a long life.

18:46.240 --> 18:48.110
Perhaps after you pass
the remaining trials,

18:48.110 --> 18:50.040
fate may bring you together again.

18:53.720 --> 18:54.850
What's the plan now?

18:57.680 --> 18:59.080
You've lost your memory.

18:59.410 --> 19:02.670
Obviously, we go to Chongling Valley
for the bone renewal.

19:03.350 --> 19:03.790
Right.

19:04.240 --> 19:05.040
Bone renewal.

19:07.240 --> 19:08.100
Master Autumn,

19:08.270 --> 19:09.070
are you awake?

19:09.510 --> 19:10.400
Would you honor me

19:10.400 --> 19:11.660
with a cup of cold wine?

19:14.030 --> 19:14.890
Master Autumn—

19:16.360 --> 19:17.560
he's calling for you.

19:20.960 --> 19:22.160
Come, Master Autumn,

19:22.480 --> 19:23.510
let me properly introduce myself.

19:23.510 --> 19:24.790
I am Lord of Rust-Sword,

19:24.790 --> 19:26.510
ranked No. 2 on the
List of Top Martial Artists.

19:26.510 --> 19:28.070
I was blind earlier—

19:28.400 --> 19:30.860
I failed to recognize
your esteemed status.

19:35.400 --> 19:36.480
I heard you had enlisted

19:36.480 --> 19:38.160
and were stationed
at the western frontier,

19:38.160 --> 19:38.790
and I thought

19:38.790 --> 19:40.160
I'd never have the honor
of meeting you in this lifetime.

19:40.160 --> 19:41.690
To encounter you here today

19:41.920 --> 19:43.120
is truly a privilege.

19:43.680 --> 19:44.540
Master Autumn,

19:44.720 --> 19:46.450
let me offer you another toast.

19:49.200 --> 19:51.130
You are Lord of Rust-Sword, right?

19:51.750 --> 19:52.280
Exactly.

19:52.550 --> 19:54.070
The second on
the List of Top Martial Artists,

19:54.070 --> 19:55.070
Rust-Sword Peak—

19:55.070 --> 19:56.000
that would be me.

19:56.790 --> 19:58.250
Are you Master Rust, then?

20:00.400 --> 20:01.890
I'm not Master Autumn either.

20:01.890 --> 20:02.830
"Autumn Crimson Blade"

20:02.830 --> 20:03.890
is just an epithet.

20:05.880 --> 20:07.680
No wonder it sounded so awkward.

20:09.000 --> 20:10.200
Then you're Master Blade.

20:10.200 --> 20:11.600
Let us drink another cup.

20:17.920 --> 20:18.510
And you, sir—

20:18.510 --> 20:20.100
since you're a friend of Master Blade,

20:20.100 --> 20:20.640
you must possess

20:20.640 --> 20:22.110
considerable skill yourself.

20:22.110 --> 20:24.510
Might I ask what your ranking is
on the list?

20:26.590 --> 20:28.400
I am Chu Ying.

20:28.790 --> 20:30.390
Haven't you ever heard of me?

20:32.510 --> 20:33.310
I have not.

20:34.400 --> 20:35.440
Then that is as it should be.

20:35.440 --> 20:36.480
My abilities are modest—

20:36.480 --> 20:37.880
I hold no rank on the list.

20:39.680 --> 20:40.240
Great.

20:46.750 --> 20:47.550
Master Blade,

20:47.960 --> 20:48.720
to be frank,

20:49.240 --> 20:51.030
in all my years
roaming the martial world,

20:51.030 --> 20:53.480
I've encountered many exceptional talents.

20:53.480 --> 20:55.440
Even those from esteemed cultivation clans

20:55.440 --> 20:57.970
never struck me
as particularly remarkable.

20:58.920 --> 21:00.520
But you alone are different.

21:00.750 --> 21:01.550
I regard you

21:01.550 --> 21:02.920
as my lifelong role model,

21:02.920 --> 21:04.030
my fated rival,

21:04.400 --> 21:06.000
and my only worthy opponent!

21:08.270 --> 21:09.550
Feel free to say such things—

21:09.550 --> 21:11.610
but let's not actually cross blades.

21:12.160 --> 21:13.750
Charging solo into Ma Fort,

21:14.160 --> 21:16.270
eliminating the Eight Villains
at Yanhui Mountain,

21:16.270 --> 21:18.070
executing the tyrant Xu Ling
in Taizi Village—

21:18.070 --> 21:18.590
and

21:18.920 --> 21:19.650
my favorite—

21:20.030 --> 21:21.750
storming the immortal's manor
at Yunmen Pass,

21:21.750 --> 21:24.270
toppling the alchemy furnace,
and slaying the demonic cultivator.

21:24.270 --> 21:25.330
Each of these deeds

21:25.400 --> 21:26.160
is something I've dreamed of accomplishing

21:26.160 --> 21:27.090
but never could.

21:28.270 --> 21:29.730
Those were all in the past.

21:29.920 --> 21:31.920
I've left the martial world behind.

21:32.430 --> 21:33.110
Whether you've retired or not

21:33.110 --> 21:33.970
is your affair.

21:34.310 --> 21:35.270
But in my heart,

21:35.720 --> 21:37.350
my goal remains to surpass you

21:37.350 --> 21:39.950
and become the Human Race's
No. 1 martial hero.

21:41.720 --> 21:42.200
Great!

21:42.790 --> 21:45.270
Though I may lag slightly behind you,

21:46.480 --> 21:48.210
I too possess uncommon talent.

21:48.640 --> 21:49.960
Back in the day, several immortal sects

21:49.960 --> 21:51.200
sought to take me as a disciple,

21:51.200 --> 21:52.660
but I refused every offer.

21:53.310 --> 21:53.880
Why?

21:54.440 --> 21:56.030
In this era, cultivators
dominate the scene.

21:56.030 --> 21:58.110
Both court and commoners
revere the path of spiritual practice.

21:58.110 --> 21:59.480
From birth,

21:59.830 --> 22:01.200
those who lack immortal perception

22:01.200 --> 22:02.400
are deemed inferior.

22:02.880 --> 22:04.340
I find this deeply flawed.

22:04.640 --> 22:06.350
A simple, mundane life is valid.

22:06.350 --> 22:08.310
Secluded mountain cultivation is valid.

22:08.310 --> 22:10.240
Farming, trade, peddling, and labor—

22:10.240 --> 22:11.310
all are valid ways to live.

22:11.310 --> 22:13.440
Since when does a way of life
have a hierarchy?

22:13.440 --> 22:15.040
I aim to shatter this notion.

22:15.350 --> 22:16.920
I want to ascend to sainthood
through martial prowess

22:16.920 --> 22:18.070
to show the world

22:18.310 --> 22:21.040
that cultivation isn't
the only righteous path.

22:21.640 --> 22:23.640
If your dream is to be a martial hero,

22:23.960 --> 22:24.790
why did you become

22:24.790 --> 22:26.650
a bounty guard serving the court?

22:28.110 --> 22:29.910
Being a martial hero isn't easy.

22:30.030 --> 22:31.440
Food, lodging,

22:31.830 --> 22:33.160
bowls, plates,
and everything else on the road—

22:33.160 --> 22:34.290
nothing comes free.

22:34.960 --> 22:36.560
If I didn't take on side jobs,

22:36.750 --> 22:38.950
I couldn't afford to keep myself alive.

22:39.350 --> 22:41.210
Is bounty guard that profitable?

22:41.510 --> 22:42.240
Absolutely.

22:43.480 --> 22:44.140
Look at him—

22:44.510 --> 22:46.070
seems like a pathetic fellow,

22:46.070 --> 22:48.270
yet his head is worth 50 taels of silver.

22:48.510 --> 22:49.910
What crime did he commit?

22:50.160 --> 22:51.510
He's a hopeless gambling addict.

22:51.510 --> 22:52.370
Short on money,

22:52.790 --> 22:54.000
he killed the landlord's entire family,

22:54.000 --> 22:55.160
who had kindly taken him in,

22:55.160 --> 22:56.510
totaling 7 people, young and old.

22:56.510 --> 22:58.370
The youngest was just 3 years old.

22:59.200 --> 23:00.860
Then he truly deserves death.

23:01.030 --> 23:01.960
It won't be long.

23:01.960 --> 23:03.360
He's almost out of money.

23:03.790 --> 23:04.270
Hey,

23:04.960 --> 23:07.030
time to pay for today's noodles, isn't it?

23:07.030 --> 23:07.690
Alright...

23:08.070 --> 23:09.070
I... I know.

23:32.640 --> 23:33.370
Who's there?

23:44.480 --> 23:45.680
Don't be afraid, My Lord!

23:45.680 --> 23:47.010
It's not that madwoman!

23:47.720 --> 23:48.510
Good, good.

23:48.510 --> 23:49.030
Halt!

23:49.160 --> 23:49.820
Don't move!

23:58.480 --> 24:00.270
I am Lord of Rust-Sword,
a bounty guard of Dongzhou Prefecture,

24:00.270 --> 24:01.790
acting under orders from Lord Xu,
the Director of the Palace Administration,

24:01.790 --> 24:03.270
to apprehend the criminal Chen Gong.

24:03.270 --> 24:04.790
Given your official uniforms,

24:04.790 --> 24:06.400
I presume we are allies, not enemies.

24:06.400 --> 24:07.680
Inside the palanquin is
the Head Clerk of the Central Secretariat,

24:07.680 --> 24:08.280
Lord Song,

24:08.830 --> 24:10.000
passing through this area

24:10.000 --> 24:11.750
and seeking a secure place to rest.

24:11.750 --> 24:12.610
Do you know any?

24:14.030 --> 24:14.890
A secure place?

24:15.440 --> 24:16.040
Follow me.

24:23.350 --> 24:24.680
Safe Haven Inn—

24:25.590 --> 24:27.120
Your Safety is Guaranteed.

24:32.750 --> 24:33.440
Great.

24:37.350 --> 24:38.270
This is bad.

24:38.790 --> 24:40.250
That Song Qingbao is here,

24:40.640 --> 24:41.900
and he recognizes you.

24:43.270 --> 24:45.000
With one of us being a constable

24:45.550 --> 24:47.270
and the other supposed to be dead,

24:47.270 --> 24:48.600
wouldn't that be a shock

24:49.160 --> 24:52.030
if he finds out?

24:53.880 --> 24:54.480
It's fine.

24:55.640 --> 24:57.170
We'll keep our backs to him.

24:57.480 --> 24:58.410
He won't notice.

25:00.440 --> 25:00.970
Alright.

25:09.030 --> 25:09.490
My Lord,

25:10.350 --> 25:11.950
what would you prefer to eat?

25:13.110 --> 25:14.110
Anything is fine.

25:14.310 --> 25:15.350
Bring a few side dishes,

25:15.350 --> 25:16.590
two plates of steamed buns,
and a pot of wine.

25:16.590 --> 25:17.120
Be quick.

25:17.160 --> 25:17.820
Right away!

25:18.880 --> 25:19.960
Rest assured, My Lord.

25:19.960 --> 25:21.090
This place is clean.

25:21.270 --> 25:22.440
We'll leave right after the meal—

25:22.440 --> 25:23.900
there should be no issues.

25:26.000 --> 25:27.270
Assign 2 guards to keep watch outside.

25:27.270 --> 25:28.400
Rotate shifts for the meal!

25:28.400 --> 25:29.130
Understood!

25:31.310 --> 25:32.770
Enjoy your meal, My Lords.

25:35.440 --> 25:36.100
Attendant,

25:37.240 --> 25:38.310
could you preserve this for me?

25:38.310 --> 25:39.350
Don't let it spoil—

25:39.350 --> 25:40.810
I'll collect it tomorrow.

25:41.200 --> 25:43.600
You think this is a pickling jar
for garlic?

25:47.480 --> 25:48.270
Of course, Sir.

25:48.270 --> 25:49.270
Whatever you say.

25:50.350 --> 25:50.810
My Lord,

25:50.960 --> 25:52.720
even if you have no appetite,
please try to eat something.

25:52.720 --> 25:53.270
We still have

25:53.270 --> 25:54.680
a long journey ahead tonight.

25:54.680 --> 25:55.400
My stomach is in knots—

25:55.400 --> 25:56.030
I can't swallow a bite.

25:56.030 --> 25:56.960
You all go ahead.

25:57.000 --> 25:57.880
Please, eat.

25:59.680 --> 26:00.160
My Lord,

26:00.160 --> 26:01.960
are you facing some difficulty?

26:05.030 --> 26:06.240
I am Lord of Rust-Sword,

26:06.240 --> 26:07.400
a bounty guard from Dongzhou Prefecture,

26:07.400 --> 26:09.130
specializing in cases
others cannot resolve.

26:09.130 --> 26:10.680
Simply draft your case
as a formal petition,

26:10.680 --> 26:12.070
file it with the Dongzhou Prefecture,

26:12.070 --> 26:13.000
and set a bounty.

26:13.030 --> 26:14.200
I collect the payment,

26:14.200 --> 26:15.530
the task accomplished.

26:18.270 --> 26:20.160
If Dongzhou Prefecture

26:20.160 --> 26:21.620
could handle this matter,

26:22.270 --> 26:23.960
I wouldn't be so troubled.

26:25.590 --> 26:27.000
How could there be something
even Dongzhou Prefecture

26:27.000 --> 26:27.860
cannot manage?

26:30.030 --> 26:31.160
To be frank with you,

26:31.350 --> 26:32.550
I am ranked second

26:32.550 --> 26:33.590
on the List of Top Martial Artists,

26:33.590 --> 26:35.110
and my sword arts have reached perfection.

26:35.110 --> 26:36.110
As long as the compensation is right,

26:36.110 --> 26:37.770
any matter can be negotiated.

26:40.550 --> 26:42.150
This isn't a matter of money.

26:42.920 --> 26:44.680
It doesn't matter if you're the No. 2
on the List of Top Martial Artists.

26:44.680 --> 26:45.830
Even if the top-ranked warrior himself,

26:45.830 --> 26:47.160
the Autumn Crimson Blade, were here,

26:47.160 --> 26:49.820
he would fall in one move
against this opponent.

26:54.010 --> 26:55.070
Alright, alright.

27:02.510 --> 27:03.640
How much farther is it

27:03.640 --> 27:04.570
to the Xihe Camp?

27:05.000 --> 27:05.920
It's less than 100 li.

27:05.920 --> 27:06.960
If we travel through the night,

27:06.960 --> 27:07.920
we'll arrive by morning.

27:07.920 --> 27:09.110
Once we reach Xihe Camp,

27:09.110 --> 27:09.570
My Lord,

27:09.790 --> 27:11.390
you will be completely safe.

27:11.590 --> 27:13.320
My personal safety is trivial.

27:13.550 --> 27:14.510
Lord Liang

27:14.610 --> 27:15.640
ordered troops of the Xihe Camp

27:15.640 --> 27:16.830
into the city.

27:17.200 --> 27:18.550
The problem is,
he didn't seem to understand

27:18.550 --> 27:20.030
that it was utterly useless.

27:20.030 --> 27:21.760
If even Xihe Camp is useless...

27:24.200 --> 27:25.830
could it be that you've offended

27:25.830 --> 27:27.560
someone from an immortal sect?

27:30.350 --> 27:31.160
Those cultivators from immortal sects

27:31.160 --> 27:32.350
rarely emerge—

27:32.750 --> 27:34.750
they devote themselves to secluded
ascetic practice in the mountains.

27:34.750 --> 27:36.030
How did you cross them?

27:36.830 --> 27:38.270
About 6 days ago,

27:40.440 --> 27:43.750
I was ordered to return to the capital
to report my duties.

27:44.480 --> 27:46.880
On the way, I was abducted
by a female cultivator.

27:46.880 --> 27:47.510
She said

27:47.960 --> 27:49.490
that we had worked together

27:50.200 --> 27:51.830
to frame her husband,

27:52.830 --> 27:55.030
Lu Huai, leading to his wrongful death.

27:59.590 --> 28:00.110
Oh no.

28:00.790 --> 28:03.720
He couldn't be talking about Immortal Xin,
could he?

28:03.720 --> 28:05.310
I heard about the Wei County case.

28:05.310 --> 28:06.310
Everyone claimed

28:06.590 --> 28:08.480
Lu Huai colluded with grain merchants,

28:08.480 --> 28:10.350
calling him
a corrupt official and vile villain.

28:10.350 --> 28:11.590
But I've always believed

28:11.590 --> 28:13.110
that to govern,
one needs a bodhisattva's heart—

28:13.110 --> 28:15.000
yet also a thunderbolt's resolve.

28:15.000 --> 28:16.460
Moss seeds don't blossom.

28:16.640 --> 28:18.550
If Lu Huai were truly bent on corruption,

28:18.550 --> 28:19.680
how could the people of Wei County

28:19.680 --> 28:21.200
have ended up faring well at all?

28:21.200 --> 28:22.920
You speak wisely.

28:23.200 --> 28:24.400
But if that were true,

28:24.590 --> 28:25.030
then the cultivator would have

28:25.030 --> 28:27.160
slaughtered everyone
she could in Wei County.

28:27.160 --> 28:29.270
Why pursue it all the way to the capital?

28:29.270 --> 28:30.930
And who exactly are the "they"

28:31.030 --> 28:32.360
you mentioned earlier?

28:34.510 --> 28:34.970
My Lord,

28:36.240 --> 28:37.500
wine may lift spirits,

28:37.830 --> 28:39.290
but it cannot drown guilt.

28:39.680 --> 28:40.880
If you drink any more,

28:41.110 --> 28:42.040
you'll be drunk.

28:48.830 --> 28:50.030
About half a year ago,

28:50.920 --> 28:52.780
a heavy rain fell over Wei County.

28:53.680 --> 28:56.440
All nine counties in the Yong region
were destroyed.

28:56.440 --> 28:57.550
Everyone believed

28:58.160 --> 28:59.620
it was a natural disaster.

28:59.880 --> 29:00.590
In truth,

29:00.880 --> 29:02.680
it was man-made.

29:07.200 --> 29:07.960
Corruption?

29:08.820 --> 29:09.540
Yes.

29:10.400 --> 29:12.400
They replaced the stones with straw

29:12.400 --> 29:13.550
and coated them with mud,

29:13.550 --> 29:15.550
then built them into the riverbank.

29:17.110 --> 29:18.790
Once such heavy rain comes,

29:20.750 --> 29:22.510
nothing can hold it back.

29:23.640 --> 29:25.310
Every dam in the nine counties

29:26.030 --> 29:28.590
around Wei County collapsed.

29:29.480 --> 29:31.880
Countless fields of grain were destroyed.

29:32.960 --> 29:34.480
It's despicable!

29:36.160 --> 29:37.560
Absolutely despicable!

29:46.160 --> 29:47.270
Those damned officials

29:47.270 --> 29:48.640
pinned all the blame

29:48.830 --> 29:49.480
on Lu Huai,

29:49.480 --> 29:51.270
who was stationed

29:51.440 --> 29:52.840
near the dams at the time.

29:54.110 --> 29:55.550
There was no other way.

29:56.000 --> 29:57.880
The commoners demanded answers,

29:58.310 --> 29:59.370
while the powerful

29:59.640 --> 30:00.720
sought to control public sentiment

30:00.720 --> 30:01.920
and stabilize the situation.

30:01.920 --> 30:03.240
Someone had to

30:03.240 --> 30:04.370
shoulder the blame.

30:06.310 --> 30:08.920
And Lu Huai had disobeyed orders—

30:10.000 --> 30:11.880
he refrained from

30:12.550 --> 30:14.200
immediately controlling grain prices

30:14.200 --> 30:16.460
to attract merchants and ensure supply.

30:16.720 --> 30:17.240
Tell me,

30:17.680 --> 30:18.880
if you were in that position,

30:18.880 --> 30:20.350
would you side with officials

30:20.350 --> 30:21.310
who feigned

30:21.310 --> 30:22.440
compliance with regulations

30:22.440 --> 30:23.400
or with Lu Huai,

30:23.400 --> 30:24.400
who lost public support

30:24.400 --> 30:26.720
yet drew all the attention?

30:31.200 --> 30:32.530
I would choose neither.

30:33.720 --> 30:35.580
I would do as that cultivator did—

30:36.200 --> 30:37.860
take the fight to the capital.

30:43.240 --> 30:45.200
Take Lu Huai to prison.

30:47.720 --> 30:48.440
Lord Lu,

30:49.000 --> 30:50.000
this way, please.

31:00.350 --> 31:01.720
- Kill him!
- Kill him!

31:02.030 --> 31:03.510
-Corrupt official!
-Kill him!

31:03.510 --> 31:04.110
Go to hell!

31:04.790 --> 31:07.720
-May you die a terrible death!
-Die a wretched death!

31:07.750 --> 31:08.440
Kill him now!

31:08.440 --> 31:10.110
Kill that corrupt official!

31:10.440 --> 31:11.110
Kill him!

31:12.590 --> 31:13.550
Kill him!

31:14.110 --> 31:15.970
Kill that corrupt official, now!

31:16.110 --> 31:17.830
Take the fight to the capital?

31:20.350 --> 31:21.750
You're not a cultivator—

31:21.960 --> 31:23.750
how could you possibly defeat them?

31:23.750 --> 31:25.720
Should inaction be the answer just
because the task seems impossible?

31:25.720 --> 31:27.550
Where there is injustice,
we must intervene!

31:27.550 --> 31:29.160
Even if I break my head and bleed,

31:29.160 --> 31:29.790
even if my feet

31:29.790 --> 31:31.550
never cross the capital's gates—

31:31.550 --> 31:32.410
so long as I act,

31:32.470 --> 31:33.870
someone will witness it.

31:33.920 --> 31:35.400
One tells ten, and ten tell a hundred.

31:35.400 --> 31:36.110
If among those hundred,

31:36.110 --> 31:37.400
one person emerges who shares my resolve,

31:37.400 --> 31:39.070
they will storm the Imperial Court.

31:39.070 --> 31:40.070
If another rises,

31:40.070 --> 31:42.240
they will stand before
the Emperor himself.

31:42.240 --> 31:43.300
I refuse to believe

31:43.310 --> 31:44.830
such monumental injustice

31:44.830 --> 31:46.630
can simply be crushed into dust—

31:46.750 --> 31:49.350
I refuse to accept
it will never be overturned!

31:52.830 --> 31:54.890
Such noble righteousness, Warrior!

31:56.400 --> 31:57.460
I am not your equal.

32:01.310 --> 32:02.110
Indeed,

32:03.750 --> 32:05.240
when I was captured,

32:05.590 --> 32:07.070
I too felt resentment.

32:08.240 --> 32:09.900
When I revealed those 4 names,

32:10.030 --> 32:11.510
I was filled with dread.

32:12.110 --> 32:13.160
But today,

32:13.590 --> 32:15.270
hearing your words, Warrior,

32:16.200 --> 32:17.830
my heart has found peace.

32:18.640 --> 32:20.640
Every grievance has its source,
and every debt has its debtor.

32:20.640 --> 32:22.240
Those who frame the innocent

32:22.880 --> 32:24.680
will surely meet a wretched end!

32:25.850 --> 32:28.570
She said when she previously
went to the capital

32:29.150 --> 32:30.810
to plead Lu Huai's innocence,

32:31.160 --> 32:33.090
every appeal sank without a trace.

32:34.270 --> 32:35.670
Are these names correct?

32:35.920 --> 32:36.450
And then?

32:38.350 --> 32:39.160
Then...

32:40.030 --> 32:41.550
I raced back

32:41.550 --> 32:42.750
to the capital at full speed

32:42.750 --> 32:44.810
and reported the matter to the court.

32:44.830 --> 32:45.480
But no one

32:45.480 --> 32:46.640
believed me.

32:47.110 --> 32:48.350
They refused to accept

32:48.350 --> 32:50.920
that a cultivator
would interfere in mortal affairs.

32:50.920 --> 32:52.240
Even more, they couldn't believe

32:52.240 --> 32:52.880
that anyone could

32:52.880 --> 32:54.000
behead officials

32:54.030 --> 32:55.240
under the capital's

32:55.310 --> 32:56.680
heavy guard.

32:58.720 --> 32:59.790
Until that night,

33:00.680 --> 33:01.790
Lord Zhao

33:01.790 --> 33:03.350
was hosting a birthday banquet
at his residence,

33:03.350 --> 33:05.680
with countless officials in attendance.

33:05.790 --> 33:06.480
After several rounds

33:06.480 --> 33:07.830
of drinks,

33:08.960 --> 33:11.160
a sudden surge of sword energy flashed,

33:12.000 --> 33:13.160
and Lord Zhao's head

33:14.550 --> 33:15.440
was gone.

33:15.830 --> 33:17.920
Sword energy
without a trace of the attacker—

33:17.920 --> 33:19.550
it was the work of that cultivator.

33:19.550 --> 33:22.000
But that was only the beginning.

33:23.640 --> 33:25.110
In less than 2 hours,

33:26.070 --> 33:28.200
news came from the northern district:

33:28.680 --> 33:30.200
Lord Zhou,

33:30.200 --> 33:32.460
protected by layers of imperial guards,

33:32.640 --> 33:35.100
had his throat slit
by a single sword stroke.

33:43.640 --> 33:44.480
Who goes there?

33:44.480 --> 33:46.440
I'm Li Huang, the Captain of the
Northern Office Capital Guards.

33:46.440 --> 33:47.920
I'm here by the Emperor's order.

33:47.920 --> 33:50.520
May I ask if the one
in the carriage is Lord Zhou?

33:52.550 --> 33:53.010
My Lord,

33:53.440 --> 33:55.770
it's the Northern Office Capital Guards.

33:56.350 --> 33:56.830
My Lord?

33:57.920 --> 33:58.520
Lord Zhou?

34:01.920 --> 34:04.520
That serves him right!
A well-deserved death!

34:05.110 --> 34:06.240
Compared to death by a thousand cuts,

34:06.240 --> 34:08.440
a single blade was too merciful for him.

34:09.280 --> 34:10.630
The individuals on the list

34:10.630 --> 34:12.400
died one by one, in order.

34:13.000 --> 34:14.760
The third official, Lord Chen,

34:15.000 --> 34:16.320
grew frantic.

34:17.440 --> 34:19.800
Without even waiting for
an imperial decree,

34:19.800 --> 34:21.440
he fled the city

34:21.920 --> 34:23.070
under heavy guard

34:23.070 --> 34:25.070
and took refuge in the Jinming Camp.

34:34.760 --> 34:35.550
Guilty.

34:36.670 --> 34:37.929
Sentence: execution.

34:38.659 --> 34:39.550
When the court fails in its duty,

34:39.550 --> 34:41.800
the blade of justice
shall restore righteousness.

34:41.800 --> 34:42.920
You, as an official,

34:42.920 --> 34:44.760
withheld appeals and suppressed the truth—

34:44.760 --> 34:46.960
you are unworthy to share wines with me!

34:47.550 --> 34:48.280
How dare you!

34:50.480 --> 34:51.679
Let it be... let it be.

34:53.110 --> 34:54.150
50 taels per jar.

34:54.550 --> 34:55.480
Still drinking?

34:55.760 --> 34:56.690
That expensive?

34:56.920 --> 34:58.360
This inn sells safety.

34:58.710 --> 34:59.840
You sought refuge here after

34:59.840 --> 35:00.920
stirring such turmoil—

35:00.920 --> 35:02.510
of course the price is higher.

35:02.510 --> 35:03.630
Why would My Lord

35:03.630 --> 35:05.000
need your protection for his safety?

35:05.000 --> 35:05.440
That woman,

35:05.440 --> 35:07.480
as a cultivator meddling
in mortal affairs,

35:07.480 --> 35:08.630
has broken her Soul Oath

35:08.630 --> 35:10.070
and will inevitably suffer backlash.

35:10.070 --> 35:11.030
Whether she survives it

35:11.030 --> 35:12.160
remains uncertain.

35:12.360 --> 35:13.440
Even if she does,

35:13.710 --> 35:14.480
the court has already

35:14.480 --> 35:15.590
dispatched letters
to the major immortal sects—

35:15.590 --> 35:17.120
they will not stand idly by.

35:17.550 --> 35:19.070
Once their representatives arrive,

35:19.070 --> 35:20.760
her life will reach its end.

35:21.590 --> 35:22.590
Enough.

35:23.360 --> 35:25.150
If you ask me, these cultivators

35:25.150 --> 35:26.760
are nothing but trouble.

35:26.840 --> 35:28.320
The Emperor should issue a decree

35:28.320 --> 35:30.110
forbidding commoners
from practicing cultivation.

35:30.110 --> 35:32.190
That way, everyone
remains on equal footing.

35:32.190 --> 35:33.440
Even if problems arise,

35:33.440 --> 35:36.100
they wouldn't escalate
beyond control, right?

35:40.630 --> 35:41.760
My Lord, be careful!

35:54.920 --> 35:56.190
The table costs 10 taels.

35:56.190 --> 35:57.590
If you cannot pay for the damages today,

35:57.590 --> 35:58.250
you will not

35:58.960 --> 36:00.710
leave this inn.

36:17.580 --> 36:18.790
A loose tongue

36:18.080 --> 36:20.880
[Jiang Ji, Lingji Mountain]

36:19.280 --> 36:20.880
invites disaster.

36:22.400 --> 36:22.930
Don't go.

36:23.400 --> 36:24.730
You're no match for her.

36:25.670 --> 36:27.070
My sincerest apologies.

36:33.510 --> 36:35.000
My junior sister is impulsive

36:34.030 --> 36:37.940
[Lin Muhan, Lingji Mountain]

36:35.440 --> 36:36.650
and has little experience
confronting mortals.

36:36.650 --> 36:37.850
She lacks restraint—

36:38.070 --> 36:40.230
I hope you can find it in your heart
to forgive her, madam.

36:40.230 --> 36:42.590
I will cover all damages.

36:46.030 --> 36:47.510
She's not wrong, is she?

36:47.880 --> 36:49.110
You cultivators

36:49.110 --> 36:50.770
truly are a source of trouble.

36:51.280 --> 36:53.190
Does that strike a nerve?

36:53.400 --> 36:54.670
Are you ashamed enough to kill over it?

36:54.670 --> 36:56.760
Zuo Yingying, since you're here,

36:57.150 --> 36:58.410
why not show yourself?

36:58.760 --> 36:59.480
What's the point of meeting

36:59.480 --> 37:00.590
when all you do

37:00.610 --> 37:01.870
is threaten violence?

37:02.510 --> 37:03.070
We walk

37:03.070 --> 37:04.230
different paths.

37:04.670 --> 37:05.480
I merely heard

37:05.480 --> 37:06.190
the righteous path

37:06.190 --> 37:07.720
had produced a bold junior,

37:07.840 --> 37:09.770
daring to storm the capital alone,

37:09.780 --> 37:11.440
and came to see the spectacle.

37:11.800 --> 37:13.110
Who knew the first thing

37:13.110 --> 37:14.480
I'd witness was

37:14.480 --> 37:15.880
this tigress biting?

37:16.440 --> 37:17.150
Lin Muhan,

37:17.510 --> 37:18.920
she has such a terrible temper,

37:18.920 --> 37:20.590
yet you stick to her every day.

37:21.910 --> 37:24.750
Do you just have the hots for her?

37:24.770 --> 37:25.630
You vile wench!

37:48.260 --> 37:50.810
[Zuo Yingying, Qinghong Sect]

37:51.590 --> 37:52.480
Lin Muhan,

37:53.230 --> 37:54.890
you ought to keep her in check.

37:55.280 --> 37:56.150
Otherwise,

37:56.800 --> 37:58.230
someone will die.

38:25.560 --> 38:28.330
[Jin Lun]

38:36.030 --> 38:36.830
Immortal Zuo,

38:37.480 --> 38:38.480
it's been a while.

38:38.880 --> 38:39.840
Jin Lun,

38:40.840 --> 38:43.030
instead of cultivating
at Tianyin Mountain,

38:43.030 --> 38:44.400
why do you linger

38:44.400 --> 38:45.030
with them?

38:45.880 --> 38:46.740
Has your master

38:47.230 --> 38:49.430
decided not to accept you as a disciple—

38:49.880 --> 38:52.540
barring you from
the Path of Severing Emotions?

38:52.920 --> 38:53.800
Even better!

38:54.320 --> 38:56.120
Abandon this ascetic practice.

38:56.160 --> 38:57.190
Return to the desert with me

38:57.190 --> 38:58.520
and indulge in freedom.

38:59.920 --> 39:00.720
Enchantress!

39:03.070 --> 39:04.000
You're all here.

39:04.440 --> 39:06.110
Where is Nangong
from the Solar and Lunar Cavern?

39:06.110 --> 39:07.150
Can't you hear?

39:08.030 --> 39:09.440
That poser has been

39:09.440 --> 39:11.440
playing his flute outside for ages.

39:21.130 --> 39:22.780
[Nangong Guhong, Solar and Lunar Cavern]

39:34.880 --> 39:36.130
All that pride,

39:36.440 --> 39:37.710
yet so petty.

39:39.000 --> 39:40.060
Enough, all of you.

39:40.280 --> 39:41.710
Rein in your auras—

39:42.160 --> 39:43.820
we have business to attend to.

39:45.960 --> 39:48.020
Are you an official from the capital?

39:51.190 --> 39:52.900
We've been dispatched by our masters

39:52.900 --> 39:53.750
to apprehend the cultivator
in the capital

39:53.750 --> 39:54.880
who broke the rules.

39:55.070 --> 39:56.550
But having been in seclusion for so long,

39:56.550 --> 39:57.480
we've forgotten the way.

39:57.480 --> 39:58.280
May I ask

39:58.590 --> 40:00.390
how far the capital is from here?

40:02.710 --> 40:03.710
Make way, please!

40:05.630 --> 40:06.440
So you're

40:06.670 --> 40:08.550
all cultivators

40:08.550 --> 40:10.010
from the Lingji Mountain?

40:10.670 --> 40:12.550
I am Lin Muhan,

40:12.710 --> 40:14.550
young master of Lingji Mountain.

40:14.550 --> 40:16.210
Beside me is my junior sister,

40:16.400 --> 40:16.930
Jiang Ji.

40:21.510 --> 40:22.880
I am Jin Lun, an unaffiliated cultivator.

40:22.880 --> 40:23.590
And the one outside

40:23.590 --> 40:25.050
who wields music as a blade

40:25.190 --> 40:27.650
is Nangong Guhong
of Solar and Lunar Cavern.

40:32.800 --> 40:33.760
It's rather impolite

40:33.760 --> 40:35.360
to ask a lady's name

40:36.030 --> 40:37.320
so abruptly.

40:39.110 --> 40:40.800
This immortal lady is called Zuo Yingying,

40:40.800 --> 40:43.060
from the Cyan-Rainbow Sect of Beixiang.

40:43.480 --> 40:45.880
Now that all you esteemed cultivators
have arrived,

40:45.880 --> 40:48.280
I feel somewhat reassured.

40:48.590 --> 40:49.510
Could you please

40:49.510 --> 40:51.030
take that rogue cultivator away quickly?

40:51.030 --> 40:51.560
That way,

40:51.960 --> 40:53.760
I won't have to live in fear any longer.
